<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-4834] Old-style mapred interface only populates row key for first column when using wide rows</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-4834</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When using the ColumnFamilyRecordReader with the old-style Hadoop interface to iterate over wide row columns, the row key is only populated on the first column.&lt;br/&gt;
See attached tests.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
